Package LAB_06

Interface Interface.Stuff

All Superinterfaces:
Comparable<Interface.Stuff>
All Known Implementing Classes:
Button, Candy
Enclosing class:
Interface
public static interface Interface.Stuff extends Comparable<Interface.Stuff>
The Stuff interface defines the contract for any object that can be placed inside a Jar. Implementing classes must provide a way to:
  • return their size (weight, diameter, etc.),
  • compare themselves to other Stuff objects,
  • and print their information to the console.
